             was indicted for <rs id="t18170702-28-off153" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170702-28-off153" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170702-28-off153" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170702-28-victim249" type="victimName">
                           Alexander 
                           Byers
                        <interp inst="t18170702-28-victim249" type="surname" value="Byers"></interp>
