                  , and other of his family in the said dwelling-house then being), and stealing therein two table spoons, value 20s.; five tea-spoons, value 5s.; one pair of sugar-tongs, value 5s.; eleven 1l. bank-notes, and one warrant for payment of 5l.
            </rs>, his property.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170702-28-person251">
                  ELIZA 
                  BYERS
