                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170702-28-defend247 t18170702-28-punish158"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 42.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Park.</p>
